{"tid":1997803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金正恩時隔二十日再露面","createTime":"2020-05-02T02:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T03:09:56.000Z","uid":348984,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d8865ecbf0ae29ebda8b814746e459f80ee64653","tid":1997803,"uid":348984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ChHmeCS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FChHmeCS.jpg&h=9ac17123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北韓官媒指二十日未有露面的北韓領袖金正恩，昨日出席公開活動。<br />\n<br />\n朝中社報道，金正恩參加了平壤一個肥料工廠的落成典禮，強調工廠的落成同時也對金氏前領導人取得的成就予以紀念。但有關報道只有文字，提供任何影像。<br />\n<br />\n勞動黨的機關報《勞動新聞》則刊登了金正恩出席儀式並剪綵的照片。"},{"pid":"7cab962968faa429e999fe9200b8353dd32f2fc4","tid":1997803,"uid":23189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:25:51.000Z","msg":"三日後復活 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8c13c92d294a02e0192c246227533ec763ad99","tid":1997803,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:27:42.000Z","msg":"蕭生又中"},{"pid":"53dac650b77a476dc98657593fdcf5565d035a97","tid":1997803,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:29:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e50b1969792bdb23a7bb6993d38a8f540fcd631","tid":1997803,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c8c13c92d294a02e0192c246227533ec763ad99","tid":1997803,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:27:42.000Z","msg":"蕭生又中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:31:13.000Z","msg":"燈到著哂火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0c23dc918495e1b0a9ef2f4e8f81ebde8ffc94","tid":1997803,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:31:20.000Z","msg":"唔同樣"},{"pid":"2b1bbd497b46b1d0b6a98f133914a779bbfeedb3","tid":1997803,"uid":46904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0